model.name: Almeida2019 - Transcription-based circadian mechanism controls the duration of molecular clock states in response to signaling inputs

body.pre: This is a transcriptional-based mathematical model centered on linear combinations of the clock controlled elements (CCEs): E-box, R-box and D-box, used to identify the essential interactions needed to generate phase opposition between the activating CLOCK:BMAL1 and the repressing PER:CRY complexes.
